    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can daze foes with wild attacks.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Power Attack, base attack bonus +11.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can choose to take a -5 penalty on all melee attack rolls and combat maneuver checks to daze opponents you hit with your melee attacks for 1 round, in addition to the normal damage dealt by the attack. A successful Fortitude save negates the effect. The DC of this save is 10 + your base attack bonus. You must choose to use this feat before making the attack roll, and its effects last until your next turn.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>After hitting an opponent with a melee attack, you can spend 5 stamina points to attempt to daze that opponent as if using this feat.",
